# Pattern: funnel conversion as a percentage.
# Illustrates: percentage range bounded 0-100, ratio calculation, multi-event source.
Metric: Signup Conversion Rate
Description: Percentage of unique landing-page visitors who completed the signup form within the same session.
Owner: growth-team
Tags: growth, funnel, acquisition

Source: sessions, signups

Given all sessions that started in the last 7 days
  And the session had at least one landing_page_view
  And the traffic source is not "internal"

When we calculate
  Then count distinct sessions that completed signup
  And divide by total distinct sessions
  And multiply by 100 to get a percentage
  And round to 2 decimal places

The result is "Signup Conversion Rate"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 4 hours
  Null rate on session_id must be 0%
  Null rate on traffic_source must be less than 2%
  Row count must not drop more than 20% day over day
  Value must be between 0.5 and 25
  Value must not change more than 15% week over week
